The paper also discusses the use of SGD (Stochastic Gradient Descent) for training the model, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper involves the use of algorithms and computation, which suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as another likely sub-category. The paper also mentions the manipulation of data sequences, which falls under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper involves image processing, which suggests cs.CV (Computer Vision) as a possible sub-category.
